{"tid":2140431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少時13週年 ^_^","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:51:36.000Z","uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8541fe733eef3e91a2ac54b41d454d8b065f7e","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/117112327_569359167076749_3044890759634176193_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=itQlxgnfIuMAX8DyH0c&amp;oh=8729d0244b77ee6bb2c2e268a9fbfd4e&amp;oe=5F5450B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F117112327_569359167076749_3044890759634176193_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DitQlxgnfIuMAX8DyH0c%26oh%3D8729d0244b77ee6bb2c2e268a9fbfd4e%26oe%3D5F5450B2&h=8d95ec2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜少左個 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d84547636173d39a492de8e8b46bc71b098c6","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"有幸當年去到睇 TTS 現場 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd3770cef35479b102127ed44395c6ee1d041ceb","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"係咪要改叫中時喇 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"973dcfa41dd44346f624baa73023d40a0244bbbb","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"八人聚會 唔怪得要戴罩啦 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91a541e3c9e826b8ea13396c4542b38fd97c6e56","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"靜靜雞自推其實都幾好玩 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/12/133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif&h=25438751&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1099d6ad238195ac9fcc4dbeb9dd8557dc415dcd","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>不是每個人都可以叫sone</strong> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不是知道 「少時」的人就叫 &ldquo;Sone&rdquo; <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不是存了多少張少時照片的人就叫 &ldquo;Sone&rdquo; <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不是只要喜歡少時臉孔的就叫 &ldquo;Sone&rdquo; <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不是天天嚷嚷卻不動手做一件對少時有利的事的人就叫 &ldquo;Sone&rdquo; <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我曾經看過一個文章裡一位親說：喜歡少時的可以叫少時飯，但少時飯不等於Sone 。摸著心臟，好好問問自己，真的愛他們到某種地步了嗎？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1943c110e7bf8bfb99bdfdd0588b8c9b5aa1c856","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"Sone這個名字，是值得驕傲一生的名字 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這裡面包含了多少的淚水、艱辛、忍耐。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是因為那群少女，這個名字就算是在淚水裡面也在閃閃發光 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSone，不是所有人都叫Sone <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSone指你愛著那九個少女，同樣的愛著一個不少，並且在心裡清清楚楚的知道，少時，少了一個也不叫少時 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少女們走過來的多少不容易，除了我們還有誰知道？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她們憑著那一份對舞台的執念走到了現在 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了誰？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有Sone <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b63938ae548e6fb84d41ced3322bbdeefaeb96d1","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"不要輕易的擔起Sone這個名稱，但是！從你鄭重的嘴巴裡一字一句的說出你是Sone的時候，就請一輩子不要放下。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少時，光是聽見這個名字都會心痛 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少女們經歷了多少的痛苦才爬到了今天這個位置 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少女們最痛的時候不是被Anti攻擊的時候，是被Sone背叛的時候...! <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被最愛的Sone背叛的時候，被曾經的一生一世背叛的時候! <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，請你好好的想清楚再說出我是Sone這一句話好嗎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於很多人來說那只是一句平凡不過的陳述句 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但對於少時來說 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那卻是一份幸福的誓言! <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e294d455004b8609bd9b561c01c2c292ea1d48e1","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"所以，請你仔細的想清楚以後，再跟著我用最純淨的心、最堅定的心、最認真的心說出<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是Sone&rdquo; <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還記得嗎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那個在任何時候都沒哭過的小太陽 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卻在被Sone誤解的時候在黃金漁場落下了眼淚 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一邊說著 「我們是絕對絕對不會丟Sone的信的！」<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一邊用手倔強的抹著眼淚<br />\n那個在電台被ANTI攻擊20分鐘，卻還強顏歡笑的用最溫暖的笑容安慰著所有擔心她的人的x泰x <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卻在頒獎典禮上哭的泣不成聲 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那種時候不用言語，你會明白這些年來她為了少時，為了Sone到底隱忍了多少<br />\n那個外表看起來冷熱不侵的冰山女王*e*s*c* <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一樣會在悶熱的場內為台下愛著她的人用力舞蹈然後昏倒 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臉上的液體是淚水還是汗水？還是她不說的堅持？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那個在所有人都哭到崩潰的時候，還是滿臉笑容安慰隊友的權俞利 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卻在頒獎典禮結束以後，一個人躲在角落裡用證書擋住臉一個人大哭 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隊友說那個只要一開機，不管有多委屈都會馬上滿臉笑容的權俞利...<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那個平時最抽風最不安靜的小隊 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在馬上就要出道前對著漢江用超乎同齡人的眼光和聲音大喊我一定可以的！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是她的決心。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48284157e2e3f135e6994917ce38c6948d5be703","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"還有太多太多少時不為人知的秘密，在鏡頭前總是喜歡把一切美好事物都展現給我們的她們 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卻在鏡頭下忍受了所有的痛苦和艱難！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少時，還可以走多遠 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實說我們都不知道 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們不要後悔我們愛過她們 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們應該慶幸 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們愛過世界上唯一的天使 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在多少年以後你們會慢慢的淡出人們的視野 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶著你們永遠的光環，九個人流著眼淚一步一步越走越遠 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後的一絲光芒是最痛卻也最美的光芒 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最美的承諾 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是我們是Sone。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少時、Sone。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這兩個名字本來就是一體 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任再多流言和委屈都會堅守在一起的不可能分割的一體 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會永遠守在這裡望著你們踏上巔峰的背影 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一步一步日漸疲憊的腳步 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可是不管怎麼樣我就在這裡 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n化成一顆大樹 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不管是迎面吹來的沙子迷茫了眼眸 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還是大風大浪淹沒了身軀 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算是被迎面而來風沙覆蓋了全身的枝枒 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就在這裡 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要你們還在給我陽光，我就會永遠望著你們的方向 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為 我們叫Sone <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為 你們叫少時 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf6234d4fe8f24edf154d7d585ae8f2a203a55","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"上面有人問我地sone同少時係咩關係<br />\n我地係一個互相支持既朋友，但唔係普通既友誼<br />\n可能我地唔真正認識了解對方，但係我地永遠都會o係對方心中佔據一個無可取替既位置<br />\n即使到某日少時已經全部嫁哂人，生埋仔，我地都會祝福佢地，守護佢地 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反之亦然，我地永遠都係對方既天使，最純潔既守護天使 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而對於我黎講，佢地更加係夜空之中明亮既星光，劃破漆黑一片既夜空，照亮整片大地，令我既人生充滿意義（可能你地覺得誇張左，但係我就係諗到呢d野），最後，如果你問我點解中意少時，我只可以答你，因為佢地係少時 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b576913c27861f7c1890a9a306fe5610fb61845","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"因為少時 因為sone<br />\n決定 <del>不推文</del> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42624a71842b2e417d97599797caef60ec8d9e80","tid":2140431,"uid":133223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b576913c27861f7c1890a9a306fe5610fb61845","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"因為少時 因為sone<br />\n決定 <del>不推文</del> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd01513a5b12a09a3df3fd1546cc8469c840830","tid":2140431,"uid":277991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b576913c27861f7c1890a9a306fe5610fb61845","tid":2140431,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"因為少時 因為sone<br />\n決定 <del>不推文</del> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}